            <p class="font-bold">Limited Spring Scheduling Available</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-orange-100">
              Garage coating season books fast. Lock in your date now before our schedule fills.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a
          href="tel:+12562210373"
          class="bg-white text-orange-500 font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded-lg hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          Reserve Your Spot
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Comprehensive SEO Introduction -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 prose prose-lg prose-blue">
      <h2
        class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6 font-display tracking-tight"
      >
        Professional Garage Floor Coating That Outlasts Everything Else
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Your garage floor absorbs more punishment than any other surface in your home. Hot tires, road salt, chemical spills, heavy tool drops, and years of accumulated oil stains have left your concrete cracked, pitted, and impossible to clean. Every time you walk from garage to kitchen, you're tracking concrete dust and embedded grime into your living space. That bare concrete slab is actively working against you, and no amount of sweeping will fix the underlying problem. At Rittenworx, we permanently solve this with industrial-strength epoxy and flake coating systems that transform your deteriorating garage floor into a seamless, chemical-resistant surface that looks absolutely stunning and performs flawlessly for decades.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The difference between a professional garage floor coating and a hardware store DIY kit is the difference between a renovation that lasts 15+ years and one that peels off in 18 months. Our process starts where DIY kits can't: industrial diamond grinding that mechanically profiles your concrete to create thousands of microscopic anchor points for permanent coating adhesion. We then apply commercial-grade materials at 3-5 times the thickness of retail products, building a multi-layer armor system that handles hot tires, chemical spills, and heavy impacts without flinching. When our crew leaves your property, you won't just have a coated floor. You'll have a garage that rivals a professional showroom.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 mt-14">
        Why North Alabama Homeowners Are Coating Their Garage Floors Now
      </h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        The North Alabama climate puts unique stress on garage concrete. Summer heat drives tire temperatures above 200°F, and those scorching tires bond to bare concrete and cheap coatings, ripping them apart when you drive away. Winter brings moisture cycling that expands existing cracks and creates new ones. Every freeze-thaw cycle pushes your unprotected concrete closer to expensive structural repair territory. A professionally installed coating system stops this destructive cycle immediately and creates an impenetrable barrier between your concrete and everything that damages it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Beyond protection, a coated garage floor dramatically increases your usable living space and your home's resale value. Real estate agents consistently report that a professionally coated garage floor is one of the first things buyers notice during showings. It signals that the homeowner invested in quality throughout the property. Our clients regularly tell us their coated garage has become their favorite room in the house. Workshop projects, gym equipment, game nights, or simply parking on a surface you're proud of. Your garage deserves better than bare concrete, and you deserve a home that works harder for you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Coating Systems We Install</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Complete garage floor transformation from surface prep to final topcoat.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        {
          includedServices.map((category) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-100">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg
                  class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-500"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z"
                  />
                </svg>
                {category.title}
              </h3>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {category.items.map((item) => (
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-gray-700">
                    <svg
                      class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                      />
                    </svg>
                    {item}
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Coating Comparison Guide -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-blue-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8 text-gray-800">
        Garage Floor Coating Comparison Guide
      </h2>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-blue-900 text-white">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">System</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Lifespan</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Best For</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Cure Time</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">Maintenance</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {
              coatingTypes.map((coating, index) => (
                <tr class={index % 2 === 0 ? "bg-gray-50" : "bg-white"}>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-blue-900">
                    {coating.name}
                  </td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700">{coating.durability}</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700">{coating.best}</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-700">{coating.cureTime}</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3 text-gray-600 text-sm">
                    {coating.maintenance}
                  </td>
                </tr>
              ))
            }
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-gray-500 text-sm mt-4">
        Not sure which system is right for your garage? Text us a photo and we'll recommend the best option for your budget and goals.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common Problems We Solve -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Garage Floor Problems We Eliminate Permanently
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Stop living with a garage floor that embarrasses you. Here's how we fix it.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        {
          commonProblems.map((item) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
              <div class="flex gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg
                    class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      stroke-width="2"
                      d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">
                    {item.problem}
                  </h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm flex items-start gap-2">
                    <svg
                      class="w-4 h-4 text-green-500 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0"
                      fill="none"
                      stroke="currentColor"
                      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    >
                      <path
                        stroke-linecap="round"
                        stroke-linejoin="round"
                        stroke-width="2"
                        d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"
                      />
                    </svg>
                    {item.solution}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Process -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">
          Our Proven Installation Process
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A systematic approach that delivers flawless, long-lasting garage floors every single time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Timeline line -->
        <div
